The paper discusses the root causes of false negatives in intrusion detection systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The proposed methodology involves analyzing data, which could fall under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data science (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the design of next-generation IDSs, which could fall under software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and information theory (cs.SI).
